title: Print Instantly From Your Phone | HP Sprocket Printer  | HP
description:
HP Sprocket is a tiny, portable photo printer you can take virtually anywhere and instantly print 2x3 inch snapshots from your mobile phone in seconds. Learn more at: http://www.hp.com/go/hpsprocket

HP Sprocket allows you to customize photos on your phone or from social media by adding icons, text, borders, emojis and more so you can share the fun in an instant. Use the easy-to-load paper as photos or stickers so you can decorate or share.
